# ── Real project data (CONFIDENTIAL — company/office projects) ──────────────
# Every actual project instance under projects/ is PRIVATE company data and must
# NEVER be committed/pushed. Only projects/README.md (the convention doc) is kept.
# The fictional sample-project/ at the repo root stays tracked as reference.
projects/*/
!projects/README.md
